<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="spread-n">spread <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /spred/    美 /spred/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>传播；蔓延：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>prevent the spread of the disease
防止疾病的传播</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the spread of education
教育的普及</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[常用单数] (分布) 范围；幅度：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>wider</strong> the <strong>spread of</strong> a species, the better its chance of survival.
一个物种分布的范围越广，存活的几率越大。</p><footer>2011 江西</footer></div></div>